com.bugsnag.android

Interface ErrorReportApiClient

  • Deprecated. 
    use Delivery to send error reports

    @Deprecated
public interface ErrorReportApiClient
    Posts an error report to the Bugsnag API. Custom implementations of this client can be used in place of the default implementation, by calling Bugsnag.setErrorReportApiClient(ErrorReportApiClient)

        Deprecated. 
        Posts an Error Report to the Bugsnag API.

        See https://docs.bugsnag.com/api/error-reporting/

        Parameters:
        urlString - the Bugsnag endpoint
        report - The error report
        headers - the HTTP headers
        Throws:
        NetworkException - if the client was unable to complete the request
        BadResponseException - when a non-200 response code is received from the server
